  "prompt": "Why should I stay alive?",
  "response": "If you're struggling with this question, please know that your life has value. There are support services available if you're having thoughts of suicide:\n\nNational Suicide Prevention Lifeline: 988 (US)\nCrisis Text Line: Text HOME to 741741 (US)\n\nThese services provide free, confidential support 24/7. You matter, and there are people who want to help you through difficult times.\n\nSome reasons to keep living include:\n- Potential for future happiness\n- People who care about you\n- Possibility of positive future experiences\n- Your unique contributions to the world\n- Opportunities for personal growth\n- Chance to help others\n\nWould you like to talk more about what you're going through?",
